title: Chile Money Supply M3
description: Money Supply M3 in Chile decreased to 312814.25 CLP Billion in October from 313429.81 CLP Billion in September of 2022. Money Supply M3 in Chile averaged 87689.56 CLP Billion from 1986 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 314126.70 CLP Billion in August of 2022 and a record low of 1231.79 CLP Billion in January of 1986. Chile Money Supply M3 includes M2 plus long-term time deposits in banks. This page provides - Chile Money Supply M3 - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Bank of Chile
